data.description: This beautiful ranch offers a spacious open floor plan with new paint & new fixtures. The kitchen includes both desk space & bar top and opens up to a large living space/dining area combo. Through the sliding doors is an incredibly large sunroom, with its own separate heating/cooling system. Down the hall from the main living area is 2 spare bedrooms & a full bathroom. Across the hall the primary bedroom is complete with large closet and en-suite bathroom. The huge backyard is fully fenced and provides great deck space for entertaining or just enjoying the calm & quiet of this sweet property. This home is located in such a lovely little neighborhood. It is quiet & tucked away but yet surprisingly near to everything you need. Including interstate, bases, shipyard & more! Call to schedule your private showing.
